(Special Operation Unit)

127
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:14,840
SOU.

128
00:08:22,880 --> 00:08:24,040
Get over here and treat him!

129
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:32,600
Where is he hurt?

130
00:08:32,680 --> 00:08:34,080
Bullet wound to the chest.

131
