801
00:55:59,720 --> 00:56:01,280
Do you have plans to get married soon?

802
00:56:01,560 --> 00:56:04,480
Plans? I'll start planning now.

803
00:56:04,840 --> 00:56:06,080
Are you not worried?

804
00:56:07,440 --> 00:56:09,280
I'll get one of the apartment units,
no matter what.

805
00:56:09,800 --> 00:56:11,320
So you don't need to worry about that.

806
00:56:11,760 --> 00:56:13,840
I'm talking about what you saw
yesterday and today.

807
00:56:14,760 --> 00:56:15,760
If things go wrong,

808
00:56:16,280 --> 00:56:18,760
the world we knew up until yesterday
could collapse.

809
00:56:20,160 --> 00:56:21,920
Will something change if I worry?

810
00:56:23,720 --> 00:56:25,120
The world might not collapse after all.

811
00:56:39,520 --> 00:56:40,520
Ma'am.

812
00:56:41,280 --> 00:56:42,640
Where are my clothes?

813
00:56:44,480 --> 00:56:45,840
We burned them.

814
00:56:45,960 --> 00:56:47,080
I see.

815
00:56:48,520 --> 00:56:49,880
Then do I have to go home like this?

816
00:56:53,120 --> 00:56:54,840
Sae-bom! Hey.

817
00:56:55,280 --> 00:56:56,760
Are you all right? Let me see.

818
00:57:02,320 --> 00:57:04,400
You still don't trust me.

819
00:57:05,840 --> 00:57:07,360
My feelings are actually hurt.

820
00:57:08,720 --> 00:57:10,000
I'm fine. I can go home.

821
00:57:13,400 --> 00:57:14,840
I'm sorry for getting you into this.

822
00:57:16,760 --> 00:57:17,960
Your face looks gaunt.

823
00:57:18,040 --> 00:57:20,440
Really?
It's because I didn't have any breakfast.

824
00:57:22,240 --> 00:57:23,640
By the way, how did you get in here?

825
00:57:24,280 --> 00:57:25,880
Did they bring you in?
Were you bitten too?

826
00:57:25,960 --> 00:57:28,520
No, I came to save you.

827
00:57:30,560 --> 00:57:32,920
Wait here.
I have to go talk to someone quickly.

828
00:57:42,520 --> 00:57:43,520
Impressive.

829
00:57:55,040 --> 00:57:56,640
Looks like you could play baseball again.

830
00:58:02,840 --> 00:58:03,840
Is this

831
00:58:04,560 --> 00:58:05,640
that pill?

832
00:58:05,720 --> 00:58:09,800
That's right.
Apparently, it's a failed pneumonia cure.

833
00:58:09,960 --> 00:58:12,160
Tons of people have taken it,

834
00:58:12,960 --> 00:58:14,480
so it couldn't have caused the madness.

835
00:58:14,560 --> 00:58:16,120
But I promised I'd find it,
so there you go.

836
00:58:17,720 --> 00:58:19,200
Just because it was fine yesterday,

837
00:58:20,280 --> 00:58:22,160
it doesn't mean it'll still be fine today.

838
00:58:28,540 --> 00:58:29,540
I'll be off, then.

839
00:59:03,860 --> 00:59:05,700
Let's go. I'll take you home.

840
00:59:07,300 --> 00:59:10,380
Yes. He was right next to me all along.

841
00:59:14,500 --> 00:59:15,500
Yi-hyun.

842
00:59:17,420 --> 00:59:19,260
Are you seeing anyone by any chance?

843
00:59:19,820 --> 00:59:20,860
What? That's so random.

844
00:59:20,940 --> 00:59:22,420
-Are you?
-No.

845
00:59:22,500 --> 00:59:24,260
Do you snore
or grind your teeth in your sleep?

846
00:59:24,700 --> 00:59:25,740
I don't think so.

847
00:59:25,980 --> 00:59:27,100
Then how about we get married?

848
00:59:29,460 --> 00:59:33,100
Yi-hyun. Tell him you don't want me
to be punished.

849
00:59:33,740 --> 00:59:34,940
He wants to arrest me.

850
00:59:35,060 --> 00:59:36,140
Hey, Sae-bom.

851
00:59:39,340 --> 00:59:40,380
Want to go out?

852
00:59:45,540 --> 00:59:46,540
No.

853
00:59:49,020 --> 00:59:52,500
Hey, I told you that day
that I was only joking.

854
00:59:53,460 --> 00:59:54,860
I'm not joking.

855
00:59:55,940 --> 00:59:56,940
I mean it.

856
01:00:08,180 --> 01:00:12,940
=Happiness=

857
01:00:37,540 --> 01:00:38,580
(If people suddenly start going crazy...)

858
01:00:38,580 --> 01:00:39,380
(Missed Call: Wife)
(If people suddenly start going crazy...)

859
01:00:39,380 --> 01:00:40,060
(If people suddenly start going crazy...)

860
01:00:41,260 --> 01:00:43,660
You asked me to gather intel
on Han Tae-seok.

861
01:00:45,580 --> 01:00:47,180
(I really can't stand that guy.)

862
01:00:47,460 --> 01:00:49,300
I own a home now.

863
01:00:49,380 --> 01:00:52,420
(It's locked. The units on this floor
and below are public rental units,)

864
01:00:52,500 --> 01:00:53,420
(The ones on the upper floors
are for general sales.)

865
01:00:53,420 --> 01:00:54,260
(We welcome all new residents.)

866
01:00:54,260 --> 01:00:54,380
(The ones on the upper floors
are for general sales.)

867
01:00:54,860 --> 01:00:56,420
(A reporter called me.)

868
01:00:57,180 --> 01:00:58,380
There is a way

869
01:00:58,460 --> 01:01:00,380
(-to make money and stay safe.)
-Lee Seung-young!

870
01:01:00,660 --> 01:01:02,100
(There's a problem at the dormitory.)

871
01:01:02,180 --> 01:01:04,340
Where are the critically-ill patients?

872
01:01:04,980 --> 01:01:06,660
(But they're alive.)

873
01:01:07,380 --> 01:01:08,860
(If we stall, more people will be hurt.)

